<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-2185">
<p>this was a good clean interview with very nice soundbites sprinkled throughout&#8230;.we are finally seeing a cogent case for gold very abley presented&#8230;..</p>
<p>but i feel strongly compelled to correct the time frame on 1300 usd gold&#8230;..we is already there babycakes&#8230;..</p>
<p>the lbma otc market failed delivery on some large gold purchases measured in tons in late september&#8230;.otc could NOT deliver lgd gold&#8230;this is enormous&#8230;.the lbma offered to settle in fiats at 25% premium to the current spot&#8230;.the buyers said NO&#8230;.1050 * 1.25 = 1300+ usd&#8230;.it is here today&#8230;.the paper gold game is over with toto<br />
pulling the curtain back on a naked oz&#8230;..</p>
<p>it&#8217;s still not too late to sell the house, kids, or dogs for gold&#8230;..the window is fast closing&#8230;.we are in severe and permanent backwardation&#8230;.the paper gold markets conceal this fact&#8230;..and you sure ain&#8217;t going to here some big breasted babe on cnbc tell you&#8230;..</p>
</div>
